snippet.title: Celebrity Brewers
snippet.description:
Welcome to Celeb Brew!

If you are a fan of Hollywood news, sports news and more then you have come to the right place, because so are we! 
We love to make celebrity related content on the latest news, tea and updates on our favorite celebrities! We are uploading everything from drama videos, sports videos to informative news videos and at times we might get into some gossip as well!

If you would like to stay on top of the hottest news, then please kindly subscribe to our channel! And follow us on Instagram @celebritybrewers
